â”‚ PURPOSE:                                                                     â”‚
â”‚ This executive dashboard provides comprehensive financial performance       â”‚
â”‚ metrics for C-suite leadership, investors, and board members. It enables:   â”‚
â”‚                                                                              â”‚
â”‚ - Real-time revenue tracking (daily aggregations)                           â”‚
